           TESTSUITE 'GREETING AND FAREWELL (FAREWELL WILL FAIL)'           TESTCASE 'IT RETURNS HELLO, WORLD! AS GREETING'            MOVE 'GREETING' TO WS-MESSAGE-TYPE           PERFORM 2000-SPEAK           EXPECT WS-MESSAGE TO BE 'HELLO, WORLD!'           TESTCASE 'IT RETURNS GOODBYE, CRUEL WORLD! AS FAREWELL'            MOVE 'FAREWELL' TO WS-MESSAGE-TYPE           PERFORM 2000-SPEAK           EXPECT WS-MESSAGE TO BE 'GOODBYE, CRUEL WORLD!'           TESTCASE 'IT RETURNS HELLO, CLYDE! AS GREETING'           MOVE 'GREETING' TO WS-MESSAGE-TYPE           MOVE 'CLYDE' TO WS-NAME           PERFORM 2000-SPEAK           EXPECT WS-MESSAGE TO BE 'HELLO, CLYDE!'